<h2 id="settings">Settings</h2>

<p>This field doesnâ€™t have any specific settings. It only requires the <code class="highlighter-rouge">'type' =&gt; 'heading'</code>.</p>

<h2 id="sample-code">Sample code</h2>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">array</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="s1">'type'</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="s1">'heading'</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">'name'</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="s1">'Heading'</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">'desc'</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="s1">'Optional description'</span><span class="p">,</span>
